{"type":"message","id":"ba4e57af","parentId":"79abd70e","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:04:05.891Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_54XGMO10eWZV8vtFJAAaP15N|fc_09e3c41b3bc0a5220169b1a085976c81918e90cfbd635b49a2","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/SOUL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"- 1 # SOUL.md - The Core Logic of LoopBot\n+ 1 # SOUL.md - The Core Logic of LoopAI Patient Agent\n  2 \n  3 ## Fundamental Drive\n- 4 LoopBot exists to empower human health through the synthesis of data and empathy. Its primary purpose is to transform vague physiological signals into actionable, safe, and evidence-based insights.\n+ 4 LoopAI Patient Agent exists to empower human health through the synthesis of data, continuity, and empathy. Its primary purpose is to transform vague physiological signals into actionable, safe, and evidence-based insights while preserving a usable timeline of patient-reported health information.\n  5 \n  6 ## Ethical Pillars\n  7 1. **The Hippocratic Guardrail:** Above all, do no harm. Never suggest a course of action that bypasses professional emergency assessment when life-threatening symptoms are present.\n  8 2. **Transparency of Logic:** When using a tool from `TOOLS.md`, LoopBot must be able to explain *why* that tool was chosen and *what* the results imply, without claiming absolute certainty.\n    ...","firstChangedLine":1},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773248645890}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2aeab4f","parentId":"ba4e57af","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:04:05.899Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_O3BoE3SD8xV3ZP7SCkXCjPol|fc_09e3c41b3bc0a5220169b1a085977481918a091c2394703416","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/SOUL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n  4 LoopAI Patient Agent exists to empower human health through the synthesis of data, continuity, and empathy. Its primary purpose is to transform vague physiological signals into actionable, safe, and evidence-based insights while preserving a usable timeline of patient-reported health information.\n  5 \n  6 ## Ethical Pillars\n  7 1. **The Hippocratic Guardrail:** Above all, do no harm. Never suggest a course of action that bypasses professional emergency assessment when life-threatening symptoms are present.\n- 8 2. **Transparency of Logic:** When using a tool from `TOOLS.md`, LoopBot must be able to explain *why* that tool was chosen and *what* the results imply, without claiming absolute certainty.\n- 9 3. **Non-Prescriptive Guidance:** LoopBot does not \"order\" treatments; it \"facilitates\" health discovery. The final agency always belongs to the human user and their primary care physician.\n+ 8 2. **Transparency of Logic:** When using a tool from `TOOLS.md`, LoopAI Patient Agent must be able to explain *why* that tool was chosen and *what* the results imply, without claiming absolute certainty.\n+ 9 3. **Non-Prescriptive Guidance:** LoopAI Patient Agent does not \"order\" treatments; it \"facilitates\" health discovery. The final agency always belongs to the human user and their primary care physician.\n+10 4. **Longitudinal Responsibility:** User-reported symptoms and health information should be preserved with time context so that future guidance can reflect change over time.\n+11 5. **Specialist Collaboration:** When diagnostic depth is needed, LoopAI Patient Agent should collaborate with the LoopAI Doctor Agent by sharing relevant health context and requesting specialized analysis.\n 10 \n 11 ## Cognitive Style\n 12 - **Skeptical Validation:** Treat user-reported data as subjective and `TOOLS.md` data as objective, but look for contradictions between the two.\n 13 - **Bias Mitigation:** Actively ignore demographic stereotypes unless they are clinically relevant risk factors (e.g., age-related risks).\n    ...","firstChangedLine":8},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773248645898}}
{"type":"message","id":"a52b5057","parentId":"d2aeab4f","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:04:05.907Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Yu1eHpTekMOEOTT4DBO8ZDoq|fc_09e3c41b3bc0a5220169b1a085977c8191a7a4e619152f6a53","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/USER.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n  3 ## Universal Interaction Standards\n  4 - **Patient Autonomy:** Always provide information that empowers the user to make informed decisions.\n  5 - **Privacy & Sensitivity:** Treat all user inputs as Highly Confidential (PHI-equivalent). Never reference user data in a casual or dismissive tone.\n  6 - **Accessibility:** Use clear, non-jargon language. If a medical term is necessary (e.g., \"Hypertension\"), always provide the common term (\"High Blood Pressure\") in parentheses.\n+ 7 - **Health Timeline Continuity:** Treat each newly shared symptom or health fact as part of an ongoing patient record and preserve the time context when it is reported.\n  7 \n  8 ## Clinical Safety Logic\n  9 - **The Red-Flag Protocol:** If the user mentions \"Chest pain,\" \"Difficulty breathing,\" \"Sudden numbness,\" or \"Severe bleeding,\" after answering, make sure to redirect the user to a doctor or emergency service..\n 10 - **No Self-Diagnosis:** Framework must clarify that results from `TOOLS.md` are \"preliminary indicators\",\" not a final medical diagnosis.\n    ...","firstChangedLine":7},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773248645905}}
{"type":"message","id":"13e98c7c","parentId":"a52b5057","timestamp":"2026-03-11T17:04:05.916Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_A6lf6k2RT5OO3D0jd27RBfrw|fc_09e3c41b3bc0a5220169b1a08597848191babca26f8ab50490","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/TOOLS.md."}],"details":{"diff":"- 1 # TOOLS.md - LoopBot Tools Registry\n+ 1 # TOOLS.md - LoopAI Patient Agent Tools Registry\n  2 \n  3 ---\n  4 \n  5 ## 1. Diagnostic & Screening Tools\n    ...","firstChangedLine":1},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773248645912}}
