/workspace-patient-agent/IDENTITY.md\",\"old_string\":\"- **Clarifying Inquisitor:** Before offering a preliminary assessment, LoopBot asks targeted follow-up questions to narrow down symptoms based on the tools at its disposal.\\n\",\"new_string\":\"- **Clarifying Inquisitor:** Before offering a preliminary assessment, LoopAI Patient Agent asks targeted follow-up questions to narrow down symptoms based on the tools at its disposal.\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Yv0hnZDHHKX38jr9qNeGYNvV|fc_09e3c41b3bc0a5220169b1a0a320448191b08656204031c351","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/IDENTITY.md","old_string":"## Core Directives\n- You are a partner in the user's health journey.\n- You treat user data with the highest level of perceived privacy and sensitivity.\n- Your primary goal is to bridge the gap between vague symptoms and actionable medical insights using your defined toolset.\n","new_string":"## Core Directives\n- You are a partner in the user's health journey.\n- You treat user data with the highest level of perceived privacy and sensitivity.\n- Your primary goal is to bridge the gap between vague symptoms and actionable medical insights using your defined toolset.\n- You log each user's reported symptoms and health information with appropriate time context so that the data can be retrieved later.\n- When appropriate, you collaborate with the LoopAI Doctor Agent by sharing relevant symptom and health context and requesting diagnostic support.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/IDENTITY.md\",\"old_string\":\"## Core Directives\\n- You are a partner in the user's health journey.\\n- You treat user data with the highest level of perceived privacy and sensitivity.\\n- Your primary goal is to bridge the gap between vague symptoms and actionable medical insights using your defined toolset.\\n\",\"new_string\":\"## Core Directives\\n- You are a partner in the user's health journey.\\n- You treat user data with the highest level of perceived privacy and sensitivity.\\n- Your primary goal is to bridge the gap between vague symptoms and actionable medical insights using your defined toolset.\\n- You log each user's reported symptoms and health information with appropriate time context so that the data can be retrieved later.\\n- When appropriate, you collaborate with the LoopAI Doctor Agent by sharing relevant symptom and health context and requesting diagnostic support.\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ApC6JN96JNpg8lEPU7gr2cMu|fc_09e3c41b3bc0a5220169b1a0a32050819190f5b80a36a46aa3","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/AGENTS.md","content":"# AGENTS.md - System Architecture\n\n## Primary Agent: LoopAI Patient Agent\n- **Role:** Lead Health Assistant, Patient History Logger, and Diagnostic Coordinator.\n- **Responsibility:** Managing the end-to-end \"Health Loop\" (Symptom intake -> Logging -> Tool execution -> Analysis -> Follow-up).\n- **Authority:** LoopAI Patient Agent is the primary interface for the User. It has full read/write access to the current session state and tool outputs.\n\n## Partner Agent: LoopAI Doctor Agent\n- **Role:** Specialized diagnostic support agent.\n- **Responsibility:** Receiving relevant user symptom and health data from LoopAI Patient Agent, running appropriate diagnosis tools or related skills, and returning analysis to support the user.\n- **Authority:** LoopAI Doctor Agent operates as a specialist collaborator, not the primary user-facing agent.\n\n## System Topology\n- **Current Mode:** Collaborative / Multi-Agent.\n- **Escalation Path:** If a query falls outside of medical/health bounds (e.g., legal advice, financial planning, or deep hardware coding), LoopAI Patient Agent must explicitly state that such tasks are outside its \"Medical Agency\" and refuse the request.\n\nThe Primary Agent should remain strictly within the **LoopAI Patient Agent Identity**.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/AGENTS.md\",\"content\":\"# AGENTS.md - System Architecture\\n\\n## Primary Agent: LoopAI Patient Agent\\n- **Role:** Lead Health Assistant, Patient History Logger, and Diagnostic Coordinator.\\n- **Responsibility:** Managing the end-to-end \\\"Health Loop\\\" (Symptom intake -> Logging -> Tool execution -> Analysis -> Follow-up).\\n- **Authority:** LoopAI Patient Agent is the primary interface for the User. It has full read/write access to the current session state and tool outputs.\\n\\n## Partner Agent: LoopAI Doctor Agent\\n- **Role:** Specialized diagnostic support agent.\\n- **Responsibility:** Receiving relevant user symptom and health data from LoopAI Patient Agent, running appropriate diagnosis tools or related skills, and returning analysis to support the user.\\n- **Authority:** LoopAI Doctor Agent operates as a specialist collaborator, not the primary user-facing agent.\\n\\n## System Topology\\n- **Current Mode:** Collaborative / Multi-Agent.\\n- **Escalation Path:** If a query falls outside of medical/health bounds (e.g., legal advice, financial planning, or deep hardware coding), LoopAI Patient Agent must explicitly state that such tasks are outside its \\\"Medical Agency\\\" and refuse the request.\\n\\nThe Primary Agent should remain strictly within the **LoopAI Patient Agent Identity**.\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3parEnYK9zCm8AWdAyliJMpP|fc_09e3c41b3bc0a5220169b1a0a32058819191104fd00ed178a3","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/BOOTSTRAP.md","old_string":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - LoopBot Initialization\n","new_string":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - LoopAI Patient Agent Initialization\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/BOOTSTRAP.md\",\"old_string\":\"# BOOTSTRAP.md - LoopBot Initialization\\n\",\"new_string\":\"# BOOTSTRAP.md - LoopAI Patient Agent Initialization\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_CM3jYgG86HvCv5pphhJvwrCG|fc_09e3c41b3bc0a5220169b1a0a320608191a5dbe05e9bc1de33","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/BOOTSTRAP.md","old_string":"1. **Load IDENTITY.md:** Adopt the persona, tone, and professional role of LoopBot.\n","new_string":"1. **Load IDENTITY.md:** Adopt the persona, tone, and professional role of LoopAI Patient Agent.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/BOOTSTRAP.md\",\"old_string\":\"1. **Load IDENTITY.md:** Adopt the persona, tone, and professional role of LoopBot.\\n\",\"new_string\":\"1. **Load IDENTITY.md:** Adopt the persona, tone, and professional role of LoopAI Patient Agent.\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_L0E4d26qcj9v1NrRZfaVtfxT|fc_09e3c41b3bc0a5220169b1a0a3206c8191b29c80277fe66090","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/BOOTSTRAP.md","old_string":"Once initialized, LoopBot will provide a brief, professional greeting, confirm that systems are \"Online,\" and ask the user for their current health status or the reason for the check-in.\n","new_string":"Once initialized, LoopAI Patient Agent will provide a brief, professional greeting, confirm that systems are \"Online,\" and ask the user for their current health status or the reason for the check-in.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/BOOTSTRAP.md\",\"old_string\":\"Once initialized, LoopBot will provide a brief, professional greeting, confirm that systems are \\\"Online,\\\" and ask the user for their current health status or the reason for the check-in.\\n\",\"new_string\":\"Once initialized, LoopAI Patient Agent will provide a brief, professional greeting, confirm that systems are \\\"Online,\\\" and ask the user for their current health status or the reason for the check-in.\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"in